    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"recharging\" sounds nice but it doesn't change the fact that nobody is actually looking for me. i could just... stop. like, completely disappear from everything, and i don't think anyone would even notice for weeks. it's weird how easy it feels to just fade out.",
