      "content": "it does feel liberating. like, the idea that it wouldn't even be a big deal. no drama, no one crying, just... silence. like i'm just opting out of a game i never wanted to play anyway. do you think it would just be a quiet way to go? like, if someone finally realized i was gone, would it even feel like a loss?",
